          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
